A shewing in generall wordis that a sawle corruptithe with synne hit must be waishid and clensid from the filthe of sinne…'! The Charter of our eritage! Foure thingis be nedefull to evere Cristen man and woman to rule theein be to obtayne the blisse of heuen! Here is the mirroure of sinnes! Theis be the wordis that our saueoure Iehsu spake to his holy spouse and virgen Sent Moll! Here beginneth a tretes of mekeues! Here foloing be the artikill of the faith! "Mirror of St Edmund! imperfect"! "treatise on 'fowre maner of wasshingis!' imperfect"! Iehsu the sonne of mare mylde! Ho sumener saith this praier in the worship of the passion shall haue C. 3ere of pardon! the pardon of the monastery of Shene whiche is Syon! Here is foling a short and a frutefull tretes how that ther was assembelid viii wide men and masters for to declare what meret tribulacion is for manne mekely sufferd! Prose Life of St Catherine!
